		<h2><img src="/design/knowledge/images/document.gif" alt="document" />&nbsp;<a href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/Call-for-Proposals-CTA-Top-20-Innovations-for-Smallholder-farmers">Call for Proposals: CTA Top 20 Innovations for Smallholder farmers</a></h2>
	<br class="cl" />
	</div>
																					<p>
<div class="clear"></div>


<!-- ****************** Begin image ****************** -->
<table align="left" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="141">
<tr>

<!-- Spacer left --> <!-- End spacer -->

