<!-- Begin spacer right -->	<td rowspan="99"><img src="/design/knowledge/images/www-onepixel-trans.gif" border="0" width="7" height="1" /></td> <!-- End spacer -->
  

</tr>
</table>
<!-- ****************** End image ****************** -->

	To capture the ideas and harness the potential of ACP innovators, the Technical Centre for Agriculture&nbsp;and Rural Cooperation ACP-EU (CTA) launched a call for proposals, in December 2013, to unearth and&nbsp;award 20 TOP innovations that are transforming smallholder farms in Africa, the Caribbean and The&nbsp;Pacific.&nbsp;</p><p><i>Journalists from ACP countries are welcome to engage in this one-of-its-kind contest by interviewing both innovators and end-users.</i></p><p>Download the press release (PDF) below.&nbsp;</p>
						<p><span class="date">17/06/2014</span></p>
		<div class="cnt">
		<a class="document" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Press-Release-CTA-TOP-20-Innovations">Read more...</a>
	</div>
	<br class="cl">
</div>
			

