	<br class="cl" />
	</div>
																					<p>CTA TOP 20 Innovations - submission by country (June 2014)</p>
						<p><span class="date">17/06/2014</span></p>
		<div class="cnt">
		<a class="document" href="/Media/Multimedia/CTA-TOP-20-Innovations-submission-by-country-June-2014">Read more...</a>
	</div>
	<br class="cl">
